application.summary:
A cross platform command line interface for todo.txt.

This is a re-write of the todo.txt-cli by Gina Trapani. This implementation conforms to the todo.txt format specfication defined by Gina Trapani. For details of the todo.txt Format and the original todo.txt-cli see links below.

todo.txt Format: {blue https://github.com/todotxt/todo.txt}
todo.txt-cli: {blue https://github.com/todotxt/todo.txt-cli}

{bold.green Powered by NodeJS.}
